longBusinessSummary: INMA Holding Company Q.P.S.C. invests in shares and bonds in Qatar. It operates through three segments: Brokerage, Real Estate, and Others. The Brokerage segment provides financial brokerage services. The Real Estate segment offers property management, marketing, and sales services for real estate. The company was formerly known as Islamic Holding Group (Q.P.S.C). INMA Holding Company Q.P.S.C. was founded in 2003 and is based in Doha, Qatar.
